title: The Old Skool Masters - Ratpack Vs. Nicky Blackmarket - mp3 - 32
description:
The Old Skool Masters - Ratpack Vs. Nicky Blackmarket

........................
Released: 1998
Label: Rumour Records
Bitrate: 320kbs
........................

RATPACK are DJ Lipmaster Mark & MC Evenson Allen who joined forces back in 1986 at the birth of the warehouse/rave scene and are still standing strong 18 years later.

As Ratpack they have played throughout the UK at the defining events that have shaped the dance scene as we know now - Fantazia, Rezerection, Biology, Interdance, to current events at Helter Skelter, Moondance, United Dance, Dreamscape...and taking their sound world wide from Australia, Japan, USA, Eastern Europe and the Mediterranean building a die-hard fan base. When they play at multi-room events you can be guaranteed that their room 'packs out' when they take to the stage! Following the success of The Old Skool Masters series where they went head to head in the mix with Nicky Blackmarket, Magika and Simon 'Bassline' Smith.

Nicky Blackmarket Intro:
Real Name: Nicky Andersson-Gylden
Profile: Major UK drum & bass / jungle DJ

Manic spam eating DJ/producer, king of the swingers, the jungle VIP. Nick is famous for teaching kids how to cross the road, having a good morning and driving adults round the bend. Half owner of Black Market shop, and super quick DJ he is the man who works wonders on the decks, while his sandwiches are underneath them.
